snippet.textDisplay: What poppycock that there is little supporting evidence of giants.  Ever heard of the mound builders of Michigan and surrounding areas. The Navajo and other nearby tribes have legends of Redhaired giants living in their region as well and complete and detailed accounts of their demise at the hands of the tribal peoples. The recent investigations of that cave show that at least part of the legend is true,. Strangely, they were in my dream protecting me from some assailant. There were two of them that marched in step and came straight for him, reached into the second story of the dilapidated house, grabbed him and tossed him right out. They were head to toe, soldiers, complete with Roman helmets and shields etc, down to their sandals. The bad guy was ironically Arab looking and dressed in a sultan sized large black turban - he was dressed for those times. Aside from the strange details of the dream, the most significant aspect is that i recently did my DNA test and learned that I have Sardinian ancestors. I, at first, dismissed this trivial since many times small amounts could be erroneous.. but recently one of my uncles had his DNA test done and guess what blood line also showed up in his? Sardinian.... I would have NEVER thought we had that ancestry in our bloodline... but apparently we do...and that dream tells me it's more of a significant find than not.
